# Development Server — Docs Prototypes

This folder contains HTML prototypes. Use `live-server` for local development with hot reload.

## Start the server

```bash
cd /Users/jvargas/Documents/GitHub/best-day-phone/docs/design && npx --yes live-server --port=5500
```

## Server details

- **URL:** http://127.0.0.1:5500/
- **Port:** 5500
- **Hot reload:** Enabled (auto-refreshes on file changes)

## Notes

- Run the server in the background when developing
- Changes to HTML, CSS, and JS files will auto-refresh the browser
- No build step required — static HTML files
